citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:45 p.m. on
15-JAN-20.
No contact was made with any person at the facility. A message was left on the cell phone of record. The licensee
returned the call at approximately 3:30 p.m.
